data.description: Ask how you can receive 1% back for closing or rate buy down! Great starter home! Welcome to this cute 1400 square foot home. Something nice and simple for the family. This 3 bed 2 bath home has a nice layout and is equipped with Vinyl flooring in the main areas. A separate dining room makes the floor plan flow nicely. Enjoy privacy with no rear neighbors. Tax Rate only 1.8 which can help dramatically with your payment! Come and take a tour today! Agent to verify schools and measurements. See offer instructions for more information and associated docs
